00:13:41,420 --> 00:13:44,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊？那你怎么浑身都湿透了</font>

275
00:13:45,330 --> 00:13:47,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">没什么  这只是汗而已</font>

276
00:13:49,070 --> 00:13:52,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那全都是汗？不会吧</font>

277
00:13:52,740 --> 00:13:57,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">哎呀  我有阵子没有慢跑  搞不太清程度</font>

278
00:13:57,380 --> 00:13:59,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">好像是把节奏弄错了</font>

279
00:14:00,530 --> 00:14:02,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">意外地长呢</font>

280
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:04,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">42.195公里</font>

281
00:14:04,940 --> 00:14:07,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你去跑全程马拉松了吗！</font>

282
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:10,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你看啊  今天是庆祝黄金周开始的慢跑</font>

283
00:14:11,070 --> 00:14:12,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">就当是传递圣火了</font>

284
00:14:13,020 --> 00:14:16,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">传递圣火也不会跑42.195公里好不好</font>

285
00:14:16,190 --> 00:14:17,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊  累死我了</font>

286
00:14:17,820 --> 00:14:20,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">而且喉咙干死了  喝水喝水</font>

287
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:28,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">好了  冲个澡去吧</font>

288
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:30,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊  火怜妹妹</font>

289
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:32,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">什么事啊  哥哥</font>

290
00:14:32,340 --> 00:14:34,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">有件事想请教你一下</font>

291
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:38,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">什么啊  哥哥也决心走上空手道之路了吗</font>

292
00:14:38,590 --> 00:14:41,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不  想请教你的不是什么奥义</font>

293
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:48,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你是怎么判断自己是否爱恋  是否喜欢上一个人的呢</font>

294
00:14:49,090 --> 00:14:51,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">哈？什么嘛  恋爱话题啊</font>

295
00:14:52,430 --> 00:14:56,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">看到他时  心想「能给他生个小孩就好了」</font>

296
00:14:57,020 --> 00:14:59,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那不就是喜欢上了吗</font>

297
00:15:22,260 --> 00:15:23,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">Yahho  阿良良木君</font>

298
00:15:24,290 --> 00:15:26,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">Yeah～过得好吗</font>

299
00:15:28,990 --> 00:15:32,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">Yahho…Yeah…过得还好…</font>

300
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:39,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那个…</font>

301
00:15:41,220 --> 00:15:42,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那个啊  阿良良木君</font>

302
00:15:57,790 --> 00:16:02,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">都高中生了还掀人家裙子  你在想什么啊阿良良木君</font>

303
00:16:03,150 --> 00:16:04,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那个  羽川</font>

304
00:16:04,670 --> 00:16:05,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我知道啦</font>

305
00:16:06,140 --> 00:16:06,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">来</font>

306
00:16:08,100 --> 00:16:09,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你真善良  阿良良木君</font>

307
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:14,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">真是个善良的好人呢</font>

308
00:16:15,330 --> 00:16:19,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我呢  很喜欢阿良良木君的这点呢</font>

309
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:22,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">去散步吧  就一小会</font>

310
00:16:27,060 --> 00:16:30,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">阿良良木君好像是有妹妹吧</font>

311
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:31,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊</font>

312
00:16:33,220 --> 00:16:35,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">有不嫌多没有不嫌少的妹妹倒有两个</font>

313
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:36,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">怎么这么说…</font>

314
00:16:37,090 --> 00:16:40,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">但话说回来  毕竟是家人  关系倒也不紧张</font>

315
00:16:41,070 --> 00:16:44,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">可被找上很多麻烦却是真的</font>

316
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:49,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不过  我其实也给她们找过一点麻烦</font>

317
00:16:50,180 --> 00:16:53,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">彼此彼此的意思吗  不错嘛  多有家人的感觉</font>

318
00:16:53,570 --> 00:16:54,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">家人？</font>

319
00:16:54,300 --> 00:16:55,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">嗯  Family</font>

320
00:16:55,790 --> 00:16:58,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我说过我是独生女吧</font>

321
00:16:58,210 --> 00:16:59,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不  没听你说过</font>

322
00:17:00,210 --> 00:17:04,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">就是说啊  阿良良木君  我是没有家人的</font>

323
00:17:06,510 --> 00:17:10,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">喂喂  羽川  没有兄弟姐妹就叫没有家人是不是太过了</font>

324
00:17:11,260 --> 00:17:14,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">爸爸妈妈啊  爷爷奶奶的…</font>

325
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">没有</font>

326
00:17:15,730 --> 00:17:18,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">爸爸也好妈妈也好都是</font>

327
00:17:19,260 --> 00:17:20,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我都没有</font>

328
00:17:25,010 --> 00:17:29,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">就是说  妈妈的结婚对象的再婚对象就是我现在的妈妈</font>

329
00:17:29,970 --> 00:17:33,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">而她的再婚对象就是我现在的爸爸</font>

330
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:38,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">换句话说  你现在的父母并不是亲生父母的意思吗</font>

331
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:45,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">对  现在一起生活的父母和我没一点血缘关系</font>

332
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:48,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">说白了  就是毫无关系的旁人</font>

333
00:17:50,940 --> 00:17:53,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">没有血缘却说是毫无关系的旁人</font>

334
00:17:50,950 --> 00:17:54,950
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（赤の他人：意为毫无关系的旁人，直译就是红色的他人，
文字游戏，没有血缘却说是红色的）</font>

335
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:56,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这话让吸血鬼听见一定会笑出来吧</font>

336
00:17:58,720 --> 00:17:59,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">才笑不出来呢</font>

337
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:06,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">就算没有血缘  也能成为家人  我曾经是这样想的</font>

338
00:18:06,770 --> 00:18:09,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我也曾努力和他们好好相处过</font>

339
00:18:10,690 --> 00:18:12,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">但总事与愿违呢  真的</font>

340
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:16,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">事与愿违  又无聊透顶</font>

341
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:21,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你的脸  是被谁打的？</font>

342
00:18:21,470 --> 00:18:26,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">为什么要问那种事呢  为什么阿良良木君要问这个…</font>

343
00:18:26,830 --> 00:18:32,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那是…那大概是…因为我是你的朋友吧</font>

344
00:18:33,180 --> 00:18:34,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">朋友…</font>

345
00:18:36,130 --> 00:18:41,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">既然是朋友不就该问问吗…这种时候  虽然我也不太明白</font>

346
00:18:42,190 --> 00:18:44,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">是吗…是啊  也许是</font>

347
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:47,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你能保证  不跟任何人说吗</font>

348
00:18:48,050 --> 00:18:49,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">嗯  那当然</font>

349
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:52,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不跟任何人说哦  真的是任何人都不行</font>

350
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:55,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">对你的妹妹…你的家人也要保密</font>

351
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:57,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我保…证</font>

352
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:03,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">早上  我被爸爸揍了</font>

353
00:19:04,180 --> 00:19:06,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">揍…那不是…</font>

354
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:09,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你瞧  只要想一下就能明白  阿良良木君</font>

355
00:19:10,690 --> 00:19:16,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">如果阿良良木君到了四十岁  被一个来历不明的十七岁女孩</font>

356
00:19:16,420 --> 00:19:18,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">用什么都知道的口吻说话的话</font>

357
00:19:18,930 --> 00:19:23,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">稍微发火一下  稍微愤怒一下  又有什么奇怪的呢</font>

358
00:19:25,620 --> 00:19:28,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">怎么这样…用这么自虐般的说法</font>

359
00:19:30,740 --> 00:19:35,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">居然为不是父母的父母…为向女儿挥拳的父母辩护？</font>

360
00:19:36,770 --> 00:19:39,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这样的羽川  让作为朋友的我</font>

361
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:41,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（作为朋友）</font>

362
00:19:42,110 --> 00:19:44,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">真的感觉很难受</font>

363
00:19:45,070 --> 00:19:47,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">暴力行为没什么奇怪？你在说什么呢</font>

364
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:52,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你说这些真的不在乎么  那不是你最不能容忍的…</font>

365
00:19:52,580 --> 00:19:54,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那又有什么呢  只是一次而已</font>

366
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:58,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我们说好了  阿良良木君</font>

367
00:19:59,570 --> 00:20:01,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我们说好了吧  阿良良木君</font>

368
00:20:02,660 --> 00:20:05,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">说好了不告诉任何人了吧</font>

369
00:20:06,380 --> 00:20:11,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">但  但是…这种约定…约定  我不能…</font>

370
00:20:11,740 --> 00:20:13,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">求你了  阿良良木君</font>

371
00:20:13,790 --> 00:20:16,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这件事  请不要告诉任何人</font>

372
00:20:16,270 --> 00:20:17,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">羽川…</font>

373
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:20,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">但是我…</font>

374
00:20:20,300 --> 00:20:22,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这件事  请不要告诉任何人</font>

375
00:20:22,850 --> 00:20:25,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">只要你不说出去  我什么都愿做</font>

376
00:20:25,330 --> 00:20:26,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">咦  真的！？</font>

377
00:20:26,590 --> 00:20:29,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">羽川什么都愿做么？太棒了！</font>

378
00:20:29,420 --> 00:20:30,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">阿  阿良良木君…</font>

379
00:20:30,930 --> 00:20:31,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">唔哇  怎么办</font>

380
00:20:32,090 --> 00:20:32,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊</font>

381
00:20:32,650 --> 00:20:34,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">做什么才好  做什么才好！</font>

382
00:20:34,370 --> 00:20:34,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊</font>

383
00:20:35,070 --> 00:20:36,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">该做什么才是最好的呢</font>

384
00:20:37,110 --> 00:20:37,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊</font>

385
00:20:37,560 --> 00:20:38,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不行</font>

386
00:20:38,140 --> 00:20:38,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊</font>

387
00:20:38,580 --> 00:20:39,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">等下等下  自己先不要慌</font>

388
00:20:40,010 --> 00:20:40,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊</font>

389
00:20:40,510 --> 00:20:42,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不能头脑发热  这种时候要先冷静</font>

390
00:20:42,930 --> 00:20:43,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊</font>

391
00:20:43,520 --> 00:20:44,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">要郑重其事！</font>

392
00:20:44,630 --> 00:20:45,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊</font>

393
00:20:45,290 --> 00:20:48,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">要把这难得的机会最大限度利用！</font>

394
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:46,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊</font>

395
00:20:48,530 --> 00:20:50,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊…咦？为什么是这种反应…</font>

396
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:52,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这是那种场面吗</font>

397
00:20:53,060 --> 00:20:59,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">阿良良木君被我的真情所打动  勉强地接受约定保持沉默才对吧</font>

398
00:20:59,330 --> 00:21:01,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">真情？那是什么玩意  不懂！</font>

399
00:21:01,390 --> 00:21:01,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（「只要是阿良良木君的要求，翼老师什么都听」）</font>

400
00:21:01,980 --> 00:21:03,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">什么都行啊</font>

401
00:21:02,730 --> 00:21:03,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（谁是翼老师啊）</font>

402
00:21:03,380 --> 00:21:06,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">但这么一说还真不好决定啊</font>

403
00:21:05,770 --> 00:21:06,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（一设想让羽川玩女教师Play时的样子，不自觉就说出来了）</font>

404
00:21:06,260 --> 00:21:09,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">可恶  我的优柔寡断真让人烦恼</font>

405
00:21:09,630 --> 00:21:14,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这种时候  一口气做出决断才算是男人中的男人</font>

406
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:16,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">…不  那应该是最差劲的男人才对</font>

407
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:23,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那个  阿良良木君  刚才我们说的那些严肃沉重的话题你还记得吗</font>

408
00:21:23,570 --> 00:21:24,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不记得了</font>

409
00:21:24,460 --> 00:21:25,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不记得了啊…</font>

410
00:21:25,970 --> 00:21:27,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">阿良良木是谁</font>

